ative in the factorization from step 1; equivalently, the product (a-b)(b-c)(c-a) has the same sign as (a+b-c)(a+c-b)(b+c-a), which is positive.\",\n      \"facts_used\": [\n        \"h₁\",\n        \"h₂\",\n        \"h₃\",\n        \"step 1\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"claim\": \"a*b*(a-b)^2 + b*c*(b-c)^2 + c*a*(c-a)^2 is nonnegative.\",\n      \"reasoning\": \"Each coefficient a*b, b*c, and c*a is positive by step 2, and each square is nonnegative, so every summand is nonnegative.\",\n      \"facts_used\": [\n        \"step 2\",\n        \"squares are nonnegative\",\n        \"product of nonnegative numbers is nonnegative\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"claim\": \"E ≥ 0.\",\n      \"reasoning\": \"By step 1, E is the sum of the expression in step 4 and the expression in step 3. Both are nonnegative, so their sum is nonnegative.\",\n      \"facts_used\": [\n        \"step 1\",\n        \"step 3\",\n        \"step 4\",\n        \"sum of nonnegative numbers is nonnegative\"\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"final_answer\": \"0 ≤ a^2*b*(a - b) + b^2*c*(b - c) + c^2*a*(c - a)\"\n}\n\nProduce the JSON formalization.\n\n## Previous attempt (failed)\nYour last formalization:\n{\"theorem\":{\"variables\":[{\"name\":\"a\",\"sort\":\"Real\"},{\"name\":\"b\",\"sort\":\"Real\"},{\"name\":\"c\",\"sort\":\"Real\"}],\"hypotheses\":[\"And(0 < a, And(0 < b, 0 < c))\",\"c < a + b\",\"b < a + c\",\"a < b + c\"],\"goal\":\"0 <= a*a*b*(a - b) + b*b*c*(b - c) + c*c*a*(c - a)\"},\"functions\":[],\"lemmas\":[{\"name\":\"cyclic_factorization\",\"english\":\"Cyclic factorization of the target expression.\",\"vars\":[{\"name\":\"a\",\"sort\":\"Real\"},{\"name\":\"b\",\"sort\":\"Real\"},{\"name\":\"c\",\"sort\":\"Real\"}],\"body\":\"a*a*b*(a - b) + b*b*c*(b - c) + c*c*a*(c - a) == a*b*(a - b)*(a - b) + b*c*(b - c)*(b - c) + c*a*(c - a)*(c - a) + (a - b)*(b - c)*(c - a)*(a + b + c)\"}],\"instantiations\":[{\"lemma\":\"cyclic_factorization\",\"terms\":{\"a\":\"a\",\"b\":\"b\",\"c\":\"c\"}}]}\